{
  "abstract": "In view of the golden Jubilee Celebration of the Indian Society of Genetics and Plant Breeding this year, the AICPMIP Workshop was combined with the second National Seminar on the Genetics of Pennisetums. The National Seminar was held on 2-3 May, and the AICPMIP Workshop on 4-5 May. Both events were very well organized at the Directorate of Rice Research, Rajendranagar, Hyderabad, We present below the highlights of various sessions. ",
